      <title>JavaScript笔记</title>
      <link href="/2021/12/07/JavaScript%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2021/12/07/JavaScript%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>tips：<code>prompt()</code>取过来的值是字符型</p></blockquote><h3 id="数据类型转换"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#数据类型转换"></a> 数据类型转换</h3><p>1.转换为字符串</p><pre class="highlight"><code class="javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> num = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(num.toString);<span class="hljs-comment">// 1.toString()</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>(num));<span class="hljs-comment">// 2.String()强制转换</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(num + <span class="hljs-string">"我是字符串"</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">// 3.加号拼接字符串</span></code></pre><p>2.转换为数字型*</p><pre class="highlight"><code class="javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> age = prompt(<span class="hljs-string">'请输入您的年龄'</span>)；<span class="hljs-comment">// 获取的值为字符型</span><span class="hljs-comment">// 1.parseInt()转换为整数数值型</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">parseInt</span>(age));<span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">parseInt</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'3.14'</span>));<span class="hljs-comment">// 返回 3 （不进行四舍五入）</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">parseInt</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'120px'</span>));<span class="hljs-comment">// 返回 120</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">parseInt</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'rem120px'</span>));<span class="hljs-comment">// 返回 NaN</span><span class="hljs-comment">// 2.parseFloat()转换为浮点数数值型</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">parseFloat</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'3.14'</span>));<span class="hljs-comment">// 返回 3.14</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">parseFloat</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'120px'</span>));<span class="hljs-comment">// 返回 120</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">parseFloat</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'rem120px'</span>));<span class="hljs-comment">// 返回 NaN</span><span class="hljs-comment">// 3.Number()强制转换</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-built_in">Number</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'123'</span>));<span class="hljs-comment">// 4.利用算术运算符 - * / 隐式转换</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-string">'12'</span> - <span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<span class="hljs-comment">// 12</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-string">'12'</span> - <span class="hljs-string">'10'</span>);<span class="hljs-comment">// 2</span><span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="hljs-string">'12'</span> * <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<span class="hljs-comment">// 12</span></code></pre><p>3.转换为布尔值</p><ul><li>利用<code>Boolean()</code>强制转换</li><li><code>' '</code> <code>0</code> <code>NaN</code> <code>null</code> <code>undefined</code> 转换为 false</li><li>其余值都会被转换为true</li></ul><blockquote><p>tips：利用<code>==</code>进行比较时，默认转换数据类型，会把字符串型数据转换为数字型</p></blockquote><h3 id="短路运算逻辑中断"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#短路运算逻辑中断"></a> 短路运算（逻辑中断）</h3><p><strong>短路运算的原理</strong>：当有多个表达式（值）时，左边的表达式值可以确定结果时，就不再继续运算右边的表达式的值。</p><p>1.逻辑与</p><ul><li>语法：<code>表达式1 &amp;&amp; 表达式2</code></li><li>如果<code>表达式1</code>为真，则返回<code>表达式2</code></li><li>如果<code>表达式1</code>为假，则返回<code>表达式1</code></li></ul><p>2.逻辑或</p><ul><li>同上</li></ul><blockquote><p>tips：逻辑中断很重要，可能会影响运算结果</p></blockquote><h3 id="运算符优先级"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#运算符优先级"></a> 运算符优先级</h3><table><thead><tr><th>优先级</th><th>运算符</th><th>顺序</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>小括号</td><td><code>()</code></td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>一元运算符</td><td><code>++</code> <code>--</code> <code>!</code></td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>算数运算符</td><td>先<code>*</code> <code>/</code> <code>%</code>  后<code>+</code> <code>-</code></td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>关系运算符</td><td><code>&gt;</code> <code>&gt;=</code> <code>&lt;</code> <code>&lt;=</code></td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>相等运算符</td><td><code>==</code> <code>!=</code> <code>===</code> <code>!==</code></td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>逻辑运算符</td><td>先<code>&amp;&amp;</code>  后<code>||</code></td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>赋值运算符</td><td><code>=</code></td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>逗号运算符</td><td><code>,</code></td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
